        <a href="#faq1" class="card-link" data-toggle="collapse">
          Why does perfume smell different on different people?
        </a>
      </div>
      <div id="faq1" class="collapse show" data-parent="#accordian">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="text-muted small">Your own body chemistry affects how different notes react on your skin. Anything that affects the “natural” smell of your skin, such as stress, hormonal changes, your current diet or medications, might change how a perfume smells on you.</p>
        </div>
